{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28b01144cffeVSFQZ2hbA3EsqH","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d750b4330001ykwcYHJr4RiY0q","parts":[{"id":"prt_d750b49ad0010xZlPx7s6pFNlf","messageID":"msg_d750b4330001ykwcYHJr4RiY0q","sessionID":"ses_28b01144cffeVSFQZ2hbA3EsqH","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置完成总结\n\n### 环境配置\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Python 版本 | 3.11.2 |\n| 虚拟环境 | `/workspace/venv` |\n| 包安装 | `pip install -e \".[test,eth-extra]\"` |\n| Git Submodule | 已初始化 (fixtures, fixtures_eest) |\n\n### 依赖安装\n- **核心依赖**: eth-keys, eth-utils, eth-typing, rlp, trie, py-ecc, ckzg 等\n- **测试依赖**: pytest, pytest-asyncio, pytest-cov, hypothesis, factory-boy 等\n- **额外依赖**: coincurve, blake2b-py (eth-extra)\n\n### 验证测试结果\n\n| 测试类别 | 结果 |\n|----------|------|\n| **核心测试** (tests/core/) | ✅ 4229 passed, 223 skipped, 26 xfailed |\n| **数据库测试** (tests/database/) | ✅ 427 passed, 140 skipped, 26 xfailed |\n| **交易测试** (test_transactions.py) | ✅ 22701 passed |\n| **VM 测试** (test_virtual_machine.py) | ✅ 1182 passed, 3690 skipped |\n| **难度测试** (test_difficulty.py) | ✅ 17 passed |\n| **区块链测试-Frontier** | ✅ 252 passed |\n| **区块链测试-Homestead** | ✅ 340 passed |\n| **Lint/Pre-commit** | ✅ 所有检查通过 |\n| **Wheel 构建** | ✅ py_evm-0.12.1b1-py3-none-any.whl |\n\n### 关键命令\n```bash\n# 安装依赖\npython3 -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate\npip install -e \".[test,eth-extra]\"\n\n# 初始化 submodule\ngit submodule update --init --recursive\n\n# 运行测试\npython -m pytest tests/core/\npython -m pytest tests/database/\npython -m pytest tests/json-fixtures/\n\n# Lint 检查\npre-commit run --all-files\n\n# 构建包\npython -m build\n```\n\n### 结论\n✅ **配置验证通过** - py-evm 仓库已成功配置，所有核心测试、JSON fixtures 测试、lint 检查均通过，wheel 包构建成功。","time":{"start":1775785177244,"end":1775785177244}}]}
